      "value": "<p>&gt;@UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.class-features.Item.unJ8E4IikZUxT7x3]{Temporal Anomalies (Su)}</p>\n<p>You manipulate time to speed up your allies, freeing them from the normal bounds of time. Once per day, you can use a paradox as part of a standard action to cast @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.spells.Item.PecEOjojT15BJKi9]{Haste} as a 3rd-level spell without expending a spell slot, even if it isn’t among your known spells. When you cast haste in this way, you can target a maximum number of allies equal to your Dexterity modifier, and you can’t target yourself. At 14th level, you can use hasten ally twice per day.</p>"
